{
  "texts": [
    "Total cognition could be predicted with an accuracy of R 2 = 0.23 (MAE = 10.37), crystallised cognition with R 2 = 0.22 (MAE = 10.24) and grip strength with R 2 = 0.19 (MAE = 9.79).",
    "Similarly to age, reducing their reliability resulted in a decrease in prediction accuracy (Fig. 1b).",
    "For all three assessments, R 2 halved when simulated data reached reliability of approximately 0.6 (R 2 total cog.",
    "= 0.12; R 2 crystalized cog.",
    "= 0.1; R 2 grip strength = 0.1)."
  ]
}